description: Leafy texture, that tesselates very well, and is one of my favoriate textures. I've used it often in the past GDS website layouts.

description: Very dark texture, best used on a dark image as an overlay so it "highlights" certain parts of the dark image.

description: Good for many metal / steel plate images.
